{"tid":2268113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国低端勞工拒公司降職降薪要求  與高層領導衝突「遭滅火器爆頭」","createTime":"2020-11-02T14:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T17:38:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2231b76c8fe3fd7520ad067efe9d80d0930922be","tid":2268113,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T14:10:38.000Z","msg":"中國大陸深圳一名任職客服主管的彭姓男子近日表示，他因拒絕降職降薪與公司高管發生衝突，結果竟被後者用滅火器打爆頭，還被移出公司微信群。彭男經鑑定為輕微傷，打人者則被處以行政拘留10日、罰款人民幣200元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/06/09/realtime/8007630.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=465&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F06%2F09%2Frealtime%2F8007630.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D465%26nt%3D1&h=a7fb97f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7332/4983186?from=udn-ch1_breaknews-1-0-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7332%2F4983186%3Ffrom%3Dudn-ch1_breaknews-1-0-news&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EpwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=6c21b41b\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7332/4983186?from=udn-ch1_breaknews-1-0-news</a>"},{"pid":"779cc05765b99cf153aea8efd07fe9e549d4183e","tid":2268113,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:45:17.000Z","msg":"勞動法維權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中共國係權貴資本主義國家"},{"pid":"767cfdeb841597852715c783d122d3cb4f2b821e","tid":2268113,"uid":7206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:48:53.000Z","msg":"大陸不嬲都拳頭解決問題正常賽果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ca215ec20233b2d0108324403db0e36c0652e0","tid":2268113,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-1